data.description: Welcome to this stunning mid-century modern home located in a prime location, just 5 miles from ACU and Dyess. Inside you are greeted by an inviting open floor plan adorned with exquisite Saltillo tile, complementing the freshly painted interior and the accent stone walls throughout. The kitchen impresses with brand new matching appliances, while the updated flooring adds a touch of modern elegance. You will enjoy the custom built in cabinetry and ample storage throughout the home. Spacious primary bedroom hosts the second fireplace, room for an office and flex space off of the back leading to the patio. The exterior of the home has beautiful established landscaping. Relax in the shaded backyard with a secondary side patio fenced in seperately. Notably, this exceptional property holds a unique history, the seller shares that it was once owned by the renowned artist HC Zachry and doubled as a studio. Embrace the artistic charm and contemporary comfort of this remarkable home.
